          <p style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:14px;font-style:italic;color:var(--ink-faint);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:12px">The sample subjects above show what the tool can do. CAAFW builds course outlines and full content for any subject, any level, any format \'97 including your proprietary internal processes.</p>\
          <a href="mailto:hello@caafw.org?subject=Course%20Builder%20Enquiry&body=Subject%20I%20need%20a%20course%20for%3A%0A%0ARole%20(Learner%20%2F%20Instructor%20%2F%20Instructional%20Designer)%3A%0A%0ALevel%3A%0A%0AAny%20other%20context%3A" class="btn-secondary" style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px">Request Your Subject &rarr;</a>\
