    <h1>What is your <em>role</em><br>in this course?</h1>\
    <p class="lead">Your role shapes everything \'97 the depth, the language, and the purpose of every lesson generated.</p>\
    <div class="field-group">\
      <div class="card-grid-3">\
        <div class="sel-card" onclick="selectRole(this,'Learner')">\
          <div class="card-title">Learner</div>\
          <div class="card-sub">I want to study this subject myself. Write content I can read, follow, and learn from directly.</div>\
          <div class="card-details">\
            <div class="card-detail-item">Explanations written to build my understanding</div>\
            <div class="card-detail-item">Self-check questions and exercises</div>\
            <div class="card-detail-item">Worked examples I can follow step by step</div>\
            <div class="card-detail-item">Key terms defined precisely</div>\
          </div>\
        </div>\
        <div class="sel-card" onclick="selectRole(this,'Instructor')">\
          <div class="card-title">Instructor</div>\
