            <div class="card-detail-item">Misconceptions to address and timing guidance</div>\
          </div>\
        </div>\
        <div class="sel-card" onclick="selectRole(this,'Designer')">\
          <div class="card-title">Instructional Designer</div>\
          <div class="card-sub">I have existing process documents, SOPs, or guidelines. Convert them into structured training for staff and trainers.</div>\
          <div class="card-details">\
